sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Detector Services<br/>(indirect)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Server<br/>(indirect)

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route-name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    Note over Gateway: Loads route config<br/>Injects detector specs<br/>into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: forwarded<br/>X-Forwarded-*: forwarded<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Note over Orchestrator: Runs input detectors
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Evaluate input content
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Note over Orchestrator: Forwards to LLM
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Generate completion
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Model response
    Note over Orchestrator: Runs output detectors
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Evaluate output content
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with<br/>detections field
    alt No detections found
        Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>Original model response<br/>(OpenAI-compatible JSON)
    else Detections found
        Note over Gateway: Replaces content with<br/>route's fallback_message
        Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>Fallback message in<br/>choices[0].message.content
    end

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route-name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>stream: true<br/>Optional mTLS
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE stream (text/event-stream)
    loop Each SSE chunk
        alt No detection in chunk
            Gateway-->>Client: SSE chunk (pass-through)
        else Detection found in chunk
            Note over Gateway: Replaces with fallback_message<br/>(first detection only)
            Gateway-->>Client: SSE chunk with fallback content
        end
    end
    Gateway-->>Client: SSE: [DONE]
